---
title: Cheesy Fish Pie with mashed potato topping and garlicky peas
description: Fish pie is a hearty and comforting dish that warms the heart and soul. This particular pie features haddock smothered in a creamy sauce with a cheesy mash topping. Gorgeous green peas accompany, rounding out a beautifully balanced dish.
